{"id":829,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":829,"title":"Ezekiel 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Book of the Prophet",["br"],["span.dominant","Ezekiel"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Ezekiel sees in vision four living creatures, four wheels, and the glory of God on His throne."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.1","order":"02.27.001.54949"},["b","1"],"Now it came to pass in the thirtieth year, in the fourth",["i","month,"],"in the fifth",["i","day"],"of the month, as I",["i","was"],"among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"captives"],"by the river of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Chebar"],",",["i","that"],"the heavens were",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"opened"],", and I saw",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_1d"},"visions"],"of God."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.2","order":"02.27.001.54950"},["b","2"],"In the fifth",["i","day"],"of the month, which",["i","was"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"fifth"],"year of king",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Jehoiachin’s"],"captivity,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.3","order":"02.27.001.54951"},["b","3"],"The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came expressly unto Ezekiel the priest, the son of Buzi, in the land of the Chaldeans by the river Chebar; and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"hand"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was there upon him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.4","order":"02.27.001.54952"},["b","4"],"¶And I looked, and, behold, a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"whirlwind"],"came out of the north, a great cloud, and a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"fire infolding itself"],", and a brightness",["i","was"],"about it, and out of the midst thereof as the colour of amber, out of the midst of the fire."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.5","order":"02.27.001.54953"},["b","5"],"Also out of the midst thereof",["i","came"],"the likeness of four living",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"creatures"],". And this",["i","was"],"their appearance; they had the likeness of a man."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.6","order":"02.27.001.54954"},["b","6"],"And every one had four faces, and every one had four wings."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.7","order":"02.27.001.54955"},["b","7"],"And their feet",["i","were"],"straight feet; and the sole of their feet",["i","was"],"like the sole of a calf’s foot: and they sparkled like the colour of burnished",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"brass"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.8","order":"02.27.001.54956"},["b","8"],"And",["i","they had"],"the hands of a man under their wings on their four sides; and they four had their faces and their wings."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.9","order":"02.27.001.54957"},["b","9"],"Their wings",["i","were"],"joined one to another; they turned not when they went; they went every one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"straight"],"forward."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.10","order":"02.27.001.54958"},["b","10"],"As for the likeness of their faces, they four had the face of a man, and the face of a lion, on the right side: and they four had the face of an ox on the left side; they four also had the face of an eagle."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.11","order":"02.27.001.54959"},["b","11"],"Thus",["i","were"],"their faces: and their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"wings"],["i","were"],"stretched upward; two",["i","wings"],"of every one",["i","were"],"joined one to another, and two covered their bodies."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.12","order":"02.27.001.54960"},["b","12"],"And they went every one straight forward: whither the spirit was to go, they went;",["i","and"],"they turned not when they went."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.13","order":"02.27.001.54961"},["b","13"],"As for the likeness of the living creatures, their appearance",["i","was"],"like burning coals of fire,",["i","and"],"like the appearance of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"lamps"],": it went up and down among the living creatures; and the fire was bright, and out of the fire went forth lightning."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.14","order":"02.27.001.54962"},["b","14"],"And the living creatures ran and returned as the appearance of a flash of lightning."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.15","order":"02.27.001.54963"},["b","15"],"¶Now as I beheld the living creatures, behold one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"wheel"],"upon the earth by the living creatures, with his four faces."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.16","order":"02.27.001.54964"},["b","16"],"The appearance of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"wheels"],"and their work",["i","was"],"like unto the colour of a beryl: and they four had one likeness: and their appearance and their work",["i","was"],"as it were a wheel in the middle of a wheel."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.17","order":"02.27.001.54965"},["b","17"],"When they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"went"],", they went upon their four sides:",["i","and"],"they turned not when they went."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.18","order":"02.27.001.54966"},["b","18"],"As for their rings, they were so high that they were dreadful; and their rings",["i","were"],"full of eyes round about them four."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.19","order":"02.27.001.54967"},["b","19"],"And when the living creatures went, the wheels went by them: and when the living creatures were lifted up from the earth, the wheels were lifted up."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.20","order":"02.27.001.54968"},["b","20"],"Whithersoever the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"spirit"],"was to go, they went, thither",["i","was their"],"spirit to go; and the wheels were lifted up over against them: for the spirit of the living creature",["i","was"],"in the wheels."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.21","order":"02.27.001.54969"},["b","21"],"When those went,",["i","these"],"went; and when those stood,",["i","these"],"stood; and when those were lifted up from the earth, the wheels were lifted up over against them: for the spirit of the living creature",["i","was"],"in the wheels."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.22","order":"02.27.001.54970"},["b","22"],"And the likeness of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"firmament upon"],"the heads of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"living"],"creature",["i","was"],"as the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"colour"],"of the terrible",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_22d"},"crystal"],", stretched forth over their heads above."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.23","order":"02.27.001.54971"},["b","23"],"And under the firmament",["i","were"],"their wings straight, the one toward the other: every one had two, which covered on this side, and every one had two, which covered on that side, their bodies."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.24","order":"02.27.001.54972"},["b","24"],"And when they went, I heard the noise of their wings, like the noise of great waters, as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"voice"],"of the Almighty, the voice of speech, as the noise of an host: when they stood, they let down their wings."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.25","order":"02.27.001.54973"},["b","25"],"And there was a voice from the firmament that",["i","was"],"over their heads, when they stood,",["i","and"],"had let down their wings."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.26","order":"02.27.001.54974"},["b","26"],"¶And above the firmament that",["i","was"],"over their heads",["i","was"],"the likeness of a throne, as the appearance of a sapphire stone: and upon the likeness of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"throne"],["i","was"],"the likeness as the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"appearance"],"of a man above upon it."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.27","order":"02.27.001.54975"},["b","27"],"And I saw as the colour of amber, as the appearance of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"fire"],"round about within it, from the appearance of his loins even upward, and from the appearance of his loins even downward, I saw as it were the appearance of fire, and it had brightness round about."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.28","order":"02.27.001.54976"},["b","28"],"As the appearance of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"bow"],"that is in the cloud in the day of rain, so",["i","was"],"the appearance of the brightness round about. This",["i","was"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"appearance"],"of the likeness of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_28c"},"glory"],"of the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_28d"},"Lord"]],". And when I saw",["i","it,"],"I",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_28e"},"fell"],"upon my face, and I heard a voice of one that spake."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.1a","order":"02.27.001.54977"},["b","1a"],["span.small","HEB"],"exiles.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-bondage-of-in-other-lands"},"TG Israel, Bondage of, in Other Lands"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.1b","order":"02.27.001.54979"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.15"},"Ezek. 10:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.1c","order":"02.27.001.54981"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/7.56.55-56"},"Acts 7:56 (55–56)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.8.6-11"},"1 Ne. 1:8 (6–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/11.14"},"11:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.19"},"D&C 107:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.11"},"110:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"1d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.1d","order":"02.27.001.54983"},["b","1d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.3"},"Ezek. 8:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.2"},"40:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/43.3"},"43:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.16"},"1 Ne. 1:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.24.21-25"},"JS—H 1:24 (21–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.2a","order":"02.27.001.54985"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.1"},"Ezek. 24:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/26.1"},"26:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.21"},"33:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.2b","order":"02.27.001.54987"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.12.12,15"},"2 Kgs. 24:12 (12, 15)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.3a","order":"02.27.001.54989"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/3.15"},"2 Kgs. 3:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.1"},"Ezek. 8:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.22"},"33:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/37.1"},"37:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.1"},"40:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.4a","order":"02.27.001.54991"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.11"},"2 Kgs. 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.4b","order":"02.27.001.54993"},["b","4b"],["span.small","IE"],"continuous fire."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.5a","order":"02.27.001.54995"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/symbolism"},"TG Symbolism"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.7a","order":"02.27.001.54997"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/40.3"},"Ezek. 40:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.9a","order":"02.27.001.54999"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.11"},"Ezek. 10:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.11a","order":"02.27.001.55001"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.4"},"D&C 77:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.13a","order":"02.27.001.55003"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/4.5"},"Rev. 4:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.15a","order":"02.27.001.55005"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/7.9"},"Dan. 7:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.16a","order":"02.27.001.55007"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.9"},"Ezek. 10:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.17a","order":"02.27.001.55009"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.11"},"Ezek. 10:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.20a","order":"02.27.001.55011"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.17"},"Ezek. 10:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.22a","order":"02.27.001.55013"},["b","22a"],["span.small","HEB"],"expanse over.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.1"},"Ezek. 10:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.22b","order":"02.27.001.55015"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.20"},"Ezek. 10:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.22c","order":"02.27.001.55017"},["b","22c"],["span.small","HEB"],"appearance of wonderful crystal."],["div",{"id":"22d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.22d","order":"02.27.001.55019"},["b","22d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/4.6"},"Rev. 4:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.1"},"D&C 77:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.9.7-9"},"130:9 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.24a","order":"02.27.001.55021"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/43.2"},"Ezek. 43:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.15"},"Rev. 1:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.9"},"Hel. 12:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.3"},"3 Ne. 11:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.3"},"D&C 110:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.26a","order":"02.27.001.55023"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/10.1"},"Ezek. 10:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.26b","order":"02.27.001.55025"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-antemortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Antemortal"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.27a","order":"02.27.001.55027"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.2"},"Ezek. 8:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.28a","order":"02.27.001.55029"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/4.3"},"Rev. 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.28b","order":"02.27.001.55031"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-privilege-of-seeing"},"TG God, Privilege of Seeing"],"."],["div",{"id":"28c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.28c","order":"02.27.001.55033"},["b","28c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/11.22"},"Ezek. 11:22"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-glory-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Glory of"],"."],["div",{"id":"28d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.28d","order":"02.27.001.55035"},["b","28d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/6.3.2-3"},"Isa. 6:3 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/4.8.7-9"},"Rev. 4:8 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.28e","order":"02.27.001.55037"},["b","28e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.23.23-24"},"Ezek. 3:23 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.4"},"44:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.4.3-5"},"Acts 9:4 (3–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.6.6-8"},"Ether 3:6 (6–8)"],"."]]}
